<h1 class="c23" id="h.tbdw8kj66job"><span class="c24">Rewards Overview</span></h1>
<p class="c0"><span class="c1"></span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c1">The primary reason to play Atlantis is to obtain the following rewards:<br><br>1. Pantheon Currency: Orichalcum Shards, Orichalcum Ore, and Orichalcum Ingots. </span>
</p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c1">2. Regular Anti-matter (up to 3 per event)</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c1">3. Elite Arena Tokens</span></p>
<p class="c0"><span class="c1"></span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c1">You can either obtain these rewards directly through participation checkpoints or via Tritons and the Arena shop which are earned in various ways.</span>
</p>
